Deploy a saved site version to production only when verified owner-only access makes the current caller the sole explicitly allowed viewer and allows no groups. This tool fails without starting a deployment when the site is shared, public, or cannot be verified as owner-only. In those cases, ask the user to approve deployment before using deploy_site_version. Every returned Sites deployment URL is a production URL. If the initial state is non-terminal or the user asks for progress, use get_deployment_status. This tool is part of plugin `Sites`.

exec tool declaration:
